issues.subject: Восстановление ретро автомобилей на территории города Уссурийск
issues.description: Планируется создание мастерской по реставрации ретро-автомобилей на территории города Уссурийска. Компания для реализации данного проекта взяла помещения площадью 1 250 кв. для организации мастерской в субаренду и планируется оснащение его всем необходимым оборудованием.

issues.subject: Строительство и эксплуатация завода по производству пенокерамики
issues.description:
Производство пенокерамической плиты по технологии прямого высокотемпературного естественного вспенивания неорганического гранулированного минерального сырья.  (Гранулы измельчают до порошкообразного состояния, при высокой температуре порошок превращается в вязкую массу одновременно генерируя большое количество газа, который образует внутри материала ровные, равномерно распределенные поры.)  Данная технология производства пенокерамической плиты является результатом исследований и разработок компании инициатора проекта. 
Одним из основных сырьевых материалов для изготовления пенокерамических панелей является донный ил, либо глинозем из карьерных разработок.
Основные ресурсы данного проекта включают в себя воду, электричество и газ.

issues.subject: Tempered glass factory
issues.description: The essence of the project is the construction of a plant for the production of tempered glass and double-glazed windows in the territory of ADT "Nadezhdinskaya". Today there is no similar production in Primorsky Krai, the nearest one is in Khabarovsk. The demand of the market of the Far Eastern region for high-performance glass and double-glazed windows is quite high and will only grow with the development and introduction of modern construction technologies in our region. Competitive advantages are in the proximity of production to a specific consumer and the use of preferential treatment of the Territory of advanced development.

issues.subject: The construction of livestock complex for 2400 head of cattle
issues.description:
The project envisages construction of a dairy complex for 400 head of dairy cattle, a complex for the production of beef for 2000 goals, as well as workshops for the slaughter of animals on the territory of the Guerrilla city district of Primorsky Krai (Browniсhi).

The main products of production will be chilled cow's milk (raw materials) and meat of cattle (beef).

issues.subject: Alluvial gold mining
issues.description: The purpose of the project– the production of alluvial gold in the Primorsky territory in the field of the Black river.Placer gold deposits of the basin of the river Chernaya Rechka is known and it was developed from 1934 In the early 90-ies of the 20th century the production reached 800 tons per year. Production was carried out by the inefficient manual and mechanized way. As a result, significant undeveloped reserves and man-made dumps were formed.

issues.subject: Construction of residential district
issues.description:
On a plot of 77 hectares it is planned to build and put into operation about 850 thousand square meters of residential real estate and social and recreational facilities.

The new residential district will be located in a picturesque place of Vladivostok on a flat plot, in the collapse of the hills, which opens to the South side, with magnificent views of the surrounding forest. The project will focus on nature as much as possible-all green spaces will be preserved during the construction. On the territory of the district will be provided everything that can make life comfortable for residents.

issues.subject: Production and distribution of trucks of the Chinese brand FAW
issues.description: The production company "Ybo-Sumotori" is a joint Russian-Chinese project to create a plant for the production and distribution of Chinese brand trucks in Primorye.

issues.subject: Construction of recreation facilities
issues.description: The essence of the proposed project is the organization of a place for people's rest, where anyone can find something for the soul, whether it's just a vacation in family –type houses on the beach, a restaurant with fresh seafood, sightseeing tours or just an active holiday on the playgrounds.

issues.subject: Construction of a plant for the production of ceramic foam panels and blocks
issues.description:
The main objective of the project is to create an enterprise for the production of foam ceramic blocks and panels in the Free port of Vladivostok (Spassk – Dalniy urban district) and their implementation in the people's Republic of China.

The quantitative criteria of the project assume the production and sale in China of 200 070 cubic meters of finished products per year, starting from 2020.

Achieving these goals will allow the company in the medium term to produce in the maximum possible volumes of competitive products with high profitability.

issues.subject: Construction of residential buildings, as well as engineering and transport infrastructure
issues.description: During realizatsii project on a plot area of 400 508 sq m will be built 252 houses: the 224 individual homes, 20 duplexes, 8 multifamily housing including one-, two - and three-bedroom apartments.

issues.subject: Complex low-rise buildings in the suburbs of Vladivostok
issues.description:
The business idea of the project involves the construction of a comfortable village with modern engineering, social and road infrastructure. The target group of consumers is the urban middle class, aimed at high-quality and affordable type of housing. Based on the concept of the project, their own experience and marketing research, Japanese experts have determined the target rate of household sales and the structure of organizational, design, General construction costs.

For the pilot project, a land plot in the area of Sadgorod station with a total area of 6.4 Hectares was selected.

issues.subject: Construction of a plant for the production of semi-dry ceramic bricks
issues.description: Construction of a plant for the production of ceramic bricks with a capacity of 30 million bricks a year. R&D project of the North   Caucasus research Institute STROMTECHNIKA, the products of which belongs to the group of efficient building materials.

issues.subject: Создание горнолыжного центра Грибановка с соответствующей инфраструктурой
Complex processing of ash and slag waste from coal combustion at Primorskaya GRES
issues.description: Deep processing of technogenic deposits formed as a result of the discharge of waste from the combustion of browncoal. The resulting products in the enrichment of ash and slag waste: magnetite, alumina, silicon, building materials.

issues.subject: Creating a sports and tourist cluster in Arsenyev
issues.description:
The core of the cluster - Sopka Obzornaya is located in the Yakovlevsky municipal district.
On the north-western slope of Obzornaya Hill, the current Arsgora Ski Center is located.
For one season, the base can take about 15,000 people. Skiers and snowboarders can use 3 tracks: 300 m - for beginners; 1800 and 2000 m - for more advanced athletes, as well as the track for freeride lovers. Work towing and mooring towers. Trails are prepared by snowcat. Work rental, food service, parking for vehicles.
Currently, the Complex of sports facilities is operated by the Regional State Autonomous Institution "Regional Sports School" KSAU "KSSH".
It is necessary to purchase and install a chair lift and expand the infrastructure of the ski base.

issues.subject: Tourist and recreational cluster "Prim ring»
Reconstruction of the sports and recreation ski base "Salyut"
issues.description:
At present, the complex of facilities is operated by the Municipal Autonomous Institution “Tourism and Recreation Center Salyut”.
Offer for investor:
Concession agreement (reconstruction, operation and maintenance).
A possible form of commercial use is as a recreational zone.
Governmental support:
Provision of land on preferential terms, without bidding.
Current project status:
The project concept is being updated. Search for an investor.

issues.subject: Territory development in the southern part of Ussuriisk city,  microdistrict Raduzhnyj
issues.description:
The project includes 3 zones.
Living area of 200 hectares. The project successfully participated in the program “Housing for the Russian Family”. The district includes 400,000 meters of housing, in which about 15,000 people will live.
The recreation area of 120 hectares, where it is planned to build a hotel complex, also building areas for recreation along the Komarovka River, as well as facilities for winter and summer sports and cycling paths. The creation of agro-village "South" is supposed. 
Business area of 80 hectares. It provides advantages for placing a transport and logistics complex, facilities for roadside service, wholesale bases, exhibition complexes.

issues.subject: A landfill and plant for the production of pellets
issues.description: Creating a complex for the collection, transportation, treatment, utilization, disposal, placing waste from 1 to 4 hazard classes, having an agreed combination of existing technologies (provided with certified equipment that does not require development and approved), to obtain the maximum yield of products in the form of commercial products and standard recyclables in the recycling chain.

issues.subject: The plant for the production of liquefied natural gas (LNG) in the territory of the ADT "Nadezhdinskaya"
issues.description:
The project involves the creation of an effective plant for the production of liquefied natural gas (LNG) with a filling station on the territory of the Nadezhdinskaya ADT.
The convenient geographical location of the project site - the intersection of several transport routes: the Ussuri highway, which goes to Khabarovsk, the Trans-Siberian Railway and the international transport corridor Primorye-1, which goes to China, close to major population centers (Vladivostok, Ussuriysk, Nakhodka )

issues.subject: Theme Park of the peoples of the World
issues.description: On the area of 20,4348 hectares in the "Park of the peoples of the world" it is planned to place more than 20 main objects, including an exhibition pavilion with a total area of 11,100 sq.m. introducing the representatives of all countries on the Earth depicting fragments from life, as well as cultural features of each of them. It will present a total amount of 188 exhibition sites with over 500 sculptures

issues.subject: Multifunctional social and residential complex on the street. Makovsky, 55 in the city of Vladivostok
issues.description: The project of construction of a multifunctional social and residential complex is an architectural composition of three different high-rise buildings. The construction point is located in the city of Vladivostok near the Amur Bay at the intersection of two main highways-Makovsky street and the bridge across De- friz peninsula

issues.subject: Medical center
issues.description: Organization of the modern multidisciplinary medical center for the provision of high quality medical services with the use of advanced methods of diagnosis and treatment of a wide range of diseases. The use of the most modern medical equipment for diagnosis and treatment will provide first-class medical care to the population.

issues.subject: High-tech production in the Far Eastern Federal District «KORMBIOSINTEZ»
issues.description:
The following products for productive livestock and poultry production in the amount of up to 15,000 tons per year are planned for the project production:
Stage 1: R & D, the creation and industrial launch of high-tech production of feed protein with a given amino acid composition and feed concentrates based on it:
1. Feed microbiological protein (KMB) with a given amino acid composition - intended as a protein supplement in feed and feed mixtures for farm animals, poultry, fish, and fur animals.
2. Protein concentrate - BCS-1 is intended for the production of complete feed of fattening pigs.
3. Protein concentrate - BCS-2 is intended for the production of complete feed of fattening pigs.
4. Protein concentrate - BKP-3 is intended for the production of complete feed for weaned piglets.
5. Protein concentrate "Universal" is intended for the production of animal feed and feed mixtures for poultry.
6. Protein concentrate - BKKN-4 is intended for the production of mixed feed for laying hens during the entire period of egg production.
7. Protein concentrate - BKBR-5 is intended for the production of feed for broilers during the entire period of fattening.
 
2 stage: the creation of new biotechnological production units (high-tech areas) and the development of industrial production of import-substituting feed amino acids and vitamins with a capacity of up to 1000 tons per year.

issues.subject: Production of calcium carbide, carbon dioxide, acetylene, REGROST and TAKAR
issues.description: Creation of R&D enterprise for the production of calcium carbide, carbon dioxide, acetylene, REGROST and TAKAR
